<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了<delay20 />將美麗的煙火，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />深深地刻印在我的眼簾，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經事先潤濕好雙眼囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發射煙火時<delay8 />發出的巨大聲響，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會讓人情緒高漲呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />究竟之後還能看到<delay8 />
怎麼樣的煙火呢～！？<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />內心在雀躍不已啊～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在最喜歡的<tag a="110" b="33" />上
看到的煙火，<delay20 />看起來似乎特別漂亮呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不這麼覺得嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來就像夜空中綻放巨大的花朵，<delay20 />
超～羅曼蒂克的～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「雖然煙火很漂亮，
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<tag a="110" b="10" />更美<tag a="110" b="0" />」<pageBreak />我現在<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />強力徵求<delay20 />
能對我說出這種話的人喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想把剛剛發射的煙火，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用在未來<tag a="110" b="10" />演唱會的<delay8 />
最後一幕上呀～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最喜歡煙火<delay20 />如花朵綻放般<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發出閃光的瞬間了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火<delay20 />就快要結束了呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得帶著一絲寂寞的表情<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />凝視著剩餘煙火的我美如畫嗎！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到煙火再一下子就要結束了，<delay8 />
時間過得太快了吧～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還想再多看一點呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay8 />你看到了嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛剛的煙火<delay20 />真的超～漂亮的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>